003|// Public API specification for libseccomp Go bindings
004|// Contains public API for the bindings
005|
006|// Package seccomp provides bindings for libseccomp, a library wrapping the Linux
007|// seccomp syscall. Seccomp enables an application to restrict system call use
008|// for itself and its children.
009|package seccomp
